cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper deals with Natural Language Processing and creation of datasets for low-resourced languages. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves classification tasks, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of data augmentation techniques also suggests the possibility of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) being a relevant category. Finally, the paper deals with languages, which could potentially fall under cs.CY (Computational Linguistics).
